# Flask JWT & OAuth Pet Project

A minimal Flask application demonstrating how to work with JWT authentication and OAuth 2.0.  

### Features
- User registration and login
- JWT access and refresh tokens
- Protected routes using JWT decorators
- Basic OAuth 2.0 login example
- Simple REST API structure

### Tech Stack
- Python
- Flask
- flask-jwt-extended
- OAuth 2.0
- SQLAlchemy

### Testing
In folder /tests all tests

### Analytics and Monitoring
- Sentry
- Prometheus
- Grafana

### Run
Run file run.py